{"type": "article", "id": 23604, "title": "“月亮”椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104510jkEaMl0ixdAZGqKv.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组椅子来自澳大利亚设计师 Marcel Sigel ，一共有三款。相同点在于它的弧形座位面，让椅子多了一个转折，有了深浅光影的变化。突出的弧形结构正好在腰的位置，也很舒适。椅腿有交叉橡木腿、金属和带轮子三种，可以适应居家办公等多个环境。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045076aehMJs8SUIiuAp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104508IuhSGjMgNHciFAW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00977995\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104508sd9NaLPuYFhQrpMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03178484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104509qDHMQPmSZsKte8IU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045092atm5UsrhNFBMyJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}